data.description: Gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with all of the upgrades! The 2 story foyer welcomes you to the open floor plan with a formal dining room offering plenty of room for entertaining, large kitchen with granite countertops, beautifully stained cabinets, stainless steel appliances and decorative tile back splash. So much storage! Spacious center island that seats 10 comfortably overlooks fireside family room with built in book shelves and coffered ceiling. Large owners suite offers tray ceiling and beautiful en suite bathroom with separate tiled shower and soaking tub. Oversized secondary bedrooms and separate bonus room with skylights for extra natural light. Back yard boasts screened in sun room with vaulted ceiling, separate uncovered deck for cooking outside and view  to the level, private back yard. Close to schools and restaurants.
